### Z. Final Notes

This report is a comprehensive overview of the state of education in rural Mizoram. It highlights the progress that has been made in enrollment and infrastructure, but also the challenges that remain in improving learning outcomes. The report calls on all stakeholders to work together to ensure that every child in Mizoram receives a quality education.